'''Sharyland Independent School District''' is a public [[school district]] based in [[Mission, Texas|Mission]], [[Texas]] ([[United States|USA]]).

The district serves parts of Mission, [[Palmhurst, Texas|Palmhurst]], [[McAllen, Texas|McAllen]], and [[Alton, Texas|Alton]] as well as the unincorporated community of [[West Sharyland, Texas|West Sharyland]].

In 2009, the school district was rated "[[Texas Education Agency accountability ratings system|recognized]]" by the [[Texas Education Agency]].<ref>{{cite web|url = http://ritter.tea.state.tx.us/perfreport/account/2009/index.html|title = 2009 Accountability Rating System|publisher = Texas Education Agency}}</ref>

